Amaze
=====

Amaze is a tool to  generate mazes with triangular rooms, ordinary square rooms
and hexagonal rooms.

It consists of the command line tool amaze and the support module maze.


The amaze command line tool
---------------------------

The amaze command line tool will generate mazes of different sizes and room
layouts. The results can be saved as PDF, PNG, PS and SVG.

For a further description, run amaze --help.
